userPromptTemplate:
Generate a TOEIC Part 7 reading set.

Set type: {{setType}}

Requirements for 'single': 1 passage (150-200 words), 3-4 questions
Requirements for 'double': 2 related passages (100-150 words each), 5 questions (including 1-2 cross-passage questions)
Requirements for 'triple': 3 related passages (80-120 words each), 5 questions (including 2-3 cross-passage questions)

Passage types: business email, advertisement, article, memo, notice, online review, form, schedule, report
Question types: detail, inference, vocabulary in context, NOT stated, purpose, cross-reference

Respond with this exact JSON structure:
{
  "setType": "single|double|triple",
  "passages": [
    {
      "id": "p1",
      "textType": "string",
      "title": "string or null",
      "content": "string — full passage text"
    }
  ],
  "questions": [
    {
      "id": "q1",
      "type": "detail|inference|vocabulary|notStated|purpose|crossReference",
      "stem": "string — question text",
      "options": {"A": "string", "B": "string", "C": "string", "D": "string"},
      "correct": "A",
      "explanation": "string — reference to relevant passage section",
      "passageRef": "p1|p2|p3|cross"
    }
  ]
}
